### Frontend: `focus-track-ui` (Angular 20 Standalone)

| File | Purpose |
|------|---------|
| `core/auth/auth.ts` | AuthService: register(), login(), logout(), getToken() |
| `core/interceptors/auth.interceptor.ts` | Functional interceptor: attaches Bearer token, handles 4xx/5xx errors |
| `features/auth/login/` | Login component (TypeScript + HTML + SCSS) |
| `features/auth/register/` | Register component with confirm-password validation |
| `app.routes.ts` | `/login` → Login, `/register` → Register, wildcard → `/login` |
| `app.config.ts` | Registers `provideHttpClient(withInterceptors([authInterceptor]))` |
| `styles.scss` | Full design system: dark mode, glassmorphism card, gradient brand, animations |

